00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:28,090
who you really are,

579
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:30,820
he will surely kill you.

580
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:33,130
If you can really get out of here alive,

581
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:36,740
