600
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:27,860
For me,

601
00:38:28,440 --> 00:38:29,900
no price is too high for revenge.

602
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:31,740
The ends justify the means.

603
00:38:34,230 --> 00:38:35,170
Besides,

604
00:38:35,670 --> 00:38:38,260
